c. It will stack with Cleric or Druid HP buffs, but not the Shaman Talisman spell.<br>
d. can be purchased in enchanter, wizard, necro, mage, caster guilds<br>
<br>
Pendril's Animation<br>
a. summon pet<br>
b. requires 1 tiny dagger<br>
c. can be purchased in Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guild, Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Reclaim Energy<br>
a. Self Only Instant Mana Increase<br>
b. Banish Pet<br>
Regain Mana (50% of Pets Mana Cost)<br>
c. does not work on charmed pets<br>
d. can be purchased in enchanter, necro, mage, and caster guilds<br>
<br>
Shallow Breath<br>
a. single target DD<br>
Direct Damage (3 - 5)<br>
Decrease Strength (5)<br>
Decrease Agility (5)<br>
b. can be purchased in Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds, Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Strengthen<br>
a. single target buff<br>
Increase Strength (5 - 10)<br>
b. can be purchased in <br>
Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
Grobb, Halas, Oggok Shaman Guilds<br>
<br>
Taper Enchantment<br>
a. single target debuff<br>
Attempt to Remove 1 Spell Effect<br>
b. it is not useful against reducing the time that poison or disease effects a character<br>
c. can be purchased in Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds, Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
True North<br>
a. Self: Changes Direction to Face North<br>
b. good spell to get divination up quickly and cheaply<br>
c. can be purchased in necro, enchanter, wizard, cleric, shaman, mage, paladin, caster guilds<br>
<br>
Weaken<br>
a. single target debuff<br>
Decrease Strength (10 - 15)<br>
b. This spell also stacks with the Disempower series, but will not stack with Insipid Weakness, Enfeeblement, or Feckless Might.<br>
